Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.83,0:00:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.90,0:00:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏露你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.70,0:00:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 这怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.47,0:00:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.84,0:00:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作一点 夏露
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.81,0:00:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.57,0:00:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快叫医生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.18,0:01:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么那件事进行的如何
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.29,0:01:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 一切都还算顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.72,0:01:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就差那最后的一步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.99,0:01:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.66,0:01:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一步先别使出
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.70,0:01:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南非那边的企业
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.53,0:01:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也收购得很成功
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.67,0:01:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也又再迈进一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.71,0:01:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来有计划安排出国的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.78,0:01:29.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.57,0:01:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点神经衰弱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.34,0:01:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.94,0:02:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先给她好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.34,0:02:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏露 身体不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.91,0:02:09.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 请多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.45,0:02:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她关在房里做什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.02,0:02:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.59,0:02:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.66,0:02:20.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听说了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.16,0:02:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总有一天会明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.31,0:02:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说收购汽车公司只是个幌子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.08,0:02:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实上\N是想要南非大叶工业吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.91,0:02:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是葛萝莉亚家的生产线
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.12,0:02:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏露也受了相当的打击吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.19,0:02:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.32,0:02:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这样让夏露做下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.49,0:02:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这我都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.63,0:02:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 夏露怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.10,0:02:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽可不用知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.93,0:02:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.40,0:03:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那接下来怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.07,0:03:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.77,0:03:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好找个能做夏露工作的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.14,0:03:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来支撑这个家啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.81,0:03:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.84,0:03:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.98,0:03:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.88,0:03:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 你没这种才能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.98,0:03:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 是谁能做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.62,0:03:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了我之外
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.65,0:03:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.16,0:03:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那二人的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.46,0:03:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.79,0:03:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不知他们做得来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.27,0:03:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 他们有这个才能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.97,0:03:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也这么相信着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.01,0:03:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.37,0:03:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 我会想办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.31,0:03:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽量别引起骚动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.32,0:03:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说你做不来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.96,0:03:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈她似乎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.76,0:04:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很期望你和绮罗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.93,0:04:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和绮罗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.00,0:04:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你们两人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.57,0:04:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和葛萝莉亚家有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.64,0:04:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.78,0:04:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你当我们家的一家之主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.92,0:04:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么也愿意做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.12,0:04:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么也
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.36,0:04:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么也愿意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.23,0:04:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.76,0:04:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被看见的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.18,0:04:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.08,0:04:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.81,0:04:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我一个人静一静
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.89,0:05:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.49,0:05:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.53,0:05:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.40,0:05:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.26,0:05:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是很有威严的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.33,0:05:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威严
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.44,0:05:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.91,0:05:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是说你是这家之主
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.54,0:05:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不正确的罗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.28,0:05:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 你发现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.08,0:05:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.33,0:05:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表面上是我支持这个家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.90,0:05:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那都是夏露的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.17,0:05:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么也做不来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.31,0:06:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你…打起精神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.62,0:06:08.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.89,0:06:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有件事我必须向你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.53,0:06:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.76,0:06:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有隐藏的事未说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.37,0:06:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 你和盖鲁克先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.07,0:06:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是葛萝莉亚家的\N指定继承人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.60,0:06:25.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你们和我们结合
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.64,0:06:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们世代都会流有你的血统
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.94,0:06:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.81,0:06:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在才跟我说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.45,0:06:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.88,0:06:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不想强迫你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.35,0:06:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你能够很自然的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.25,0:06:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会想起这个家时
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.22,0:06:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.39,0:06:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我的体内
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.29,0:06:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有葛萝莉亚的血统
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.37,0:06:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姆里克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姆里克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.88,0:07:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.15,0:07:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.05,0:07:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体觉得如何
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.42,0:07:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姆里克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.93,0:07:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有看到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.93,0:07:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.90,0:07:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.87,0:07:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.07,0:07:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姆里克斯把你看做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.77,0:07:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他的母亲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.58,0:07:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能会离开你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.31,0:07:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.78,0:07:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.99,0:07:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.12,0:07:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他很喜欢你的味道嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.56,0:07:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看 别摸 别接近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.06,0:07:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.23,0:07:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电脑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.96,0:07:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.03,0:08:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 别随便乱摸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.80,0:08:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.77,0:08:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先交给我来做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.11,0:08:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.14,0:08:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像我也流着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.88,0:08:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你们一样的血统
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.85,0:08:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一样的血统
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.92,0:08:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 一样的血统
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.83,0:08:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.63,0:08:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 接下来的问题呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 说的是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.54,0:08:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南非钻石工厂的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.57,0:08:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.77,0:08:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个工厂被一家大企业
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.38,0:08:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从中偷买股权\N要将其夺走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.81,0:08:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而政府也以紧急事件处理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.62,0:08:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么一回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然钻石产量减少
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.19,0:08:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收入也将减半
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.32,0:08:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么是玛丽的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.56,0:08:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.79,0:09:01.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.23,0:09:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.96,0:09:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.83,0:09:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先减薪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.30,0:09:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再向当地政府
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.00,0:09:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.34,0:09:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道该怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.28,0:09:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.09,0:09:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚开始先这样摸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.46,0:09:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.46,0:09:34.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.06,0:09:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的变大了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.33,0:09:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想吃吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.87,0:09:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇!好大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.27,0:09:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个就像冰淇淋一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真美她说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.86,0:10:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么做的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.22,0:10:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师一定会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.88,0:10:26.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.62,0:10:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.65,0:10:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.58,0:10:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.82,0:10:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.45,0:10:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.55,0:10:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事我来做就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.02,0:10:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.56,0:10:39.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽我不行做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.03,0:10:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你问为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.36,0:10:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是一直都是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.43,0:10:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.50,0:10:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道雪希儿的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.50,0:10:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想把老师占为己有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.54,0:10:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.40,0:10:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.37,0:10:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪希儿这个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.34,0:10:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.18,0:11:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.78,0:11:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里只有玛丽是特别的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.82,0:11:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽的双亲早亡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.66,0:11:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后吃了不少苦头
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.09,0:11:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她自己什么也不说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.46,0:11:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以她来到葛萝莉亚家后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.93,0:11:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不能让她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.23,0:11:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去碰难过的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.04,0:11:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.71,0:11:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽这样没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.91,0:11:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也不能一直把她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.38,0:11:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关在温室里面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.71,0:11:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽她自己也想出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.35,0:11:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温室里起了大风
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.42,0:11:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许那就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.64,0:12:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.75,0:12:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.05,0:12:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还用说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.85,0:12:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家的当家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.39,0:12:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没这兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.62,0:12:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别装傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.09,0:12:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是当的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.89,0:12:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就有上亿的财产
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.26,0:12:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落入口袋里来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.06,0:12:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.00,0:12:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会怎样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.93,0:12:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是要财产呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.06,0:12:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是要女人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.30,0:12:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要当这家之主的路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.44,0:12:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我似乎比你快了一步
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.54,0:12:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.75,0:12:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.69,0:12:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗好像也发觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.09,0:12:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然一脸不在乎的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.66,0:12:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有份 我也有份
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.90,0:13:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是最好的结局
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.00,0:13:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点也不像你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.84,0:13:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真认真呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.57,0:13:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.47,0:13:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有时也会夸奖人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.98,0:13:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.45,0:13:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.22,0:13:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.73,0:13:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中午很对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.73,0:13:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中午
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.80,0:13:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪希儿说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.93,0:13:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师很怕雷电
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.40,0:13:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我来陪你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.35,0:13:51.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真温柔体贴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.82,0:13:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.96,0:14:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.71,0:14:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.01,0:14:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师下面的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.55,0:14:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.14,0:14:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样做 会不好意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.55,0:15:02.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.12,0:15:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.42,0:15:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.23,0:15:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.20,0:15:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很漂亮 玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.13,0:15:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.17,0:15:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.63,0:15:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.17,0:15:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.27,0:15:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽好怕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.51,0:15:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.77,0:15:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像自己不是自己的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.38,0:15:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.75,0:15:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽要改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.12,0:15:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改变
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.98,0:15:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.25,0:15:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.18,0:15:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.11,0:16:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.25,0:16:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师继续
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.38,0:16:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.51,0:16:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.55,0:16:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.22,0:16:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛 却觉得很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.52,0:16:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要到那去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.19,0:16:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.82,0:16:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就会改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.16,0:16:47.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.46,0:16:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.87,0:16:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.93,0:17:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 你醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.67,0:17:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.44,0:17:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.21,0:17:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.41,0:17:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.18,0:17:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.92,0:17:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钻石工厂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.89,0:17:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.72,0:17:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,0:17:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认识南非当地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.69,0:17:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一位很厉害的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.39,0:17:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去麻烦他的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.03,0:17:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有帮助的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.10,0:18:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.37,0:18:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是个好办法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.30,0:18:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.40,0:18:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.37,0:18:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说玛丽很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.97,0:18:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都愿意帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.01,0:18:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.88,0:18:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.98,0:18:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但大家却说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.45,0:18:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽可以不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.61,0:18:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以没说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.68,0:18:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那个人是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.75,0:18:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是南非的大总统
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.73,0:18:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.93,0:18:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个该不会是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.57,0:18:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么…你说舞会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.50,0:18:36.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.90,0:18:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.84,0:18:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使你来拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.31,0:18:41.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在对葛萝莉亚家而言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.31,0:18:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是多重要的时期
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.58,0:18:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜雪儿夫人 玛丽她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.78,0:18:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了葛萝莉亚家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.95,0:18:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想做我做得到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.18,0:18:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是夏露的姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.05,0:18:55.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.39,0:18:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你能让玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.66,0:18:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照他的想法去做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.13,0:19:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.13,0:19:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再什么也帮不上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.26,0:19:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.83,0:19:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师也会在身边的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.43,0:19:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.37,0:19:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和老师在一起的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.47,0:19:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.53,0:19:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布敏先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.63,0:19:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正等您来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.78,0:19:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 是玛丽说要办宴会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.98,0:19:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个人的主意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.35,0:19:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗那小子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.05,0:20:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在打什么主意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.69,0:20:02.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜雪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.12,0:20:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜雪儿你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.26,0:20:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你邀我来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.03,0:20:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.83,0:20:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么悠闲好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.53,0:20:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说矿场那
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.17,0:20:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快被收购走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.02,0:20:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.91,0:21:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天邀请各位来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.82,0:21:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽葛萝莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.15,0:21:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.26,0:21:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是南非的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.03,0:21:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么他们会在这
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.70,0:21:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天从南非而来的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.90,0:21:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也到了现场
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可伏克总统
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.14,0:21:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.38,0:21:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邀请我到这来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.89,0:21:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实上 今天我的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.99,0:21:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分的沉重
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.26,0:21:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为在我国的钻石产业
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.76,0:21:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,占有一席之地的葛萝莉亚家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.16,0:21:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然听说会有关闭的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.83,0:21:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那是奸商的恶性作法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.27,0:22:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那资金
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.84,0:22:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说是从布敏企业而来的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.64,0:22:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也请各位到场来宾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.35,0:22:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我国人民作证
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.58,0:22:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不让不肖奸商
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.45,0:22:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在工矿区乱收购股权
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.09,0:22:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以维护钻石产业
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.42,0:22:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此我也保证
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.89,0:22:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葛萝莉亚家在我国的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.76,0:22:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钻石产业一切如常
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.49,0:22:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不改变
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.40,0:22:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大总统
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.17,0:22:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 这样可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.71,0:22:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.68,0:22:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了小姐你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.95,0:22:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了你的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.48,0:22:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事随时可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.62,0:22:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.38,0:22:45.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.82,0:22:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你这混蛋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.15,0:22:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你全盘说出的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.02,0:22:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.29,0:22:55.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请肃静
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.56,0:22:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是葛萝莉亚家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.67,0:23:04.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这东西我先保管了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.37,0:23:08.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我也要发表
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.21,0:23:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一件重大的事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.68,0:23:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我订婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.58,0:23:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方是秋筱绮罗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.09,0:23:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被他赶上一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.76,0:23:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.64,0:23:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.02,0:23:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 请问一下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.95,0:23:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南非那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.29,0:23:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.09,0:23:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多的传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.22,0:23:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请告诉我们真相
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.66,0:24:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你说说现在的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.23,0:24:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请说
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.20,0:24:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布敏先生
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.63,0:24:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葛萝莉亚家的混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.74,0:24:16.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪希儿
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.34,0:24:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.61,0:24:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪希儿 对你…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.88,0:24:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.88,0:24:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪希儿
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.78,0:24:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.62,0:24:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.05,0:24:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.32,0:24:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时也和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.41,0:24:52.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.65,0:24:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.68,0:24:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.32,0:24:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果老师不在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.05,0:25:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便做不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.39,0:25:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…都快不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.46,0:25:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没这回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.33,0:25:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.36,0:25:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不再是老师了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.70,0:25:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,订婚了 不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.30,0:25:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们俩
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.60,0:25:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但对我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.74,0:25:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都是我的老师
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.07,0:25:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.34,0:25:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽姐姐 好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.11,0:25:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.98,0:25:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也该休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.51,0:25:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.88,0:25:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把希望放在他们身上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.92,0:26:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽她变了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.26,0:26:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.63,0:26:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好只是把她的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.23,0:26:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给发挥出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.00,0:26:25.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让人高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.64,0:26:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.21,0:26:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让人得救
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.74,0:26:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而拼命
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.81,0:26:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他那种心肠
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.55,0:26:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来当葛萝莉亚的当家
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.72,0:26:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再适合也不过了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.55,0:26:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.69,0:26:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他让我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.66,0:26:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.16,0:27:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你们

